During the course the terms of syntax are studied, as well as the methods of syntactic analysis, and the Estonian sentence structure is observed in more detail.Objectives/eesmärkid:  to give systematic overview of the Estonian Language syntax.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  1) has acquired theoretical knowledge about syntax; 2) is able to apply theoretical knowledge in practice: knows the sentence structure and can define parts of the sentence; 3) can independently compose sentence on the basis of provided scheme.
